Instructions:
take a kadhai and pour oil at high flame and add the onions and fry it till its color is golden brown.
After it is golden brown take it in a bown and add beans,cabbage and let it fry for a while
add the paneer,capsicum and 3/4 of the fried onions and low the flame.at the same time boil the rice in a cooker 
until it wistles 2-3 times.add red chille powder,pepper(optional),sewzan fried rice masala,
sause,garham masala,salt.meanwhile take a bowl and mix the corn flour with water and pour it in the 
mixture with the left over fried onions.mix the boiled rice with the mixture and ENJOY.

NOTE:TRY THIS AT HOME :)